Localead Offline Desktop App Bundle
====================================
Version: 1.0.0
Release Date: June 2026

How to run offline:
1. Extract this zip file.
2. Open terminal in the directory.
3. Run 'npm install' to install client libraries.
4. Run 'npm run dev' to start the local leads engine database.
5. Enjoy unlimited offline premium B2B lead scraping!
